{"tid":1821013,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"沈月遇勁敵！台灣20歲名媛廖思惟家世長相超優越","createTime":"2020-01-12T02:46:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-12T14:02:27.000Z","uid":209657,"like":1,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"efc765ff05a111ef839f17882cd0da825a9a3fdb","tid":1821013,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T02:46:39.000Z","msg":"提起「最美星二代」一代女神邱淑貞的大女兒沈月絕對佔一席位，今年將滿19歲的她外形出眾氣質不凡，早前更獲邀參加在巴黎隆重舉行的名媛舞會（Le Bal des D&eacute;butantes），以一身透視粉紅羽毛晚裝亮相驚艷眾人。集星二代與名媛身份於一身的她，絕對星味十足人氣更不輸當紅明星。<br />\n<br />\n不過在兩岸三地芸芸名媛中，沈月終於遇上最大勁敵。她就是台灣名媛孫芸芸的大女兒廖思惟，外形出眾身材高瘦的她既可愛又貴氣，首次亮相出席活動更成為聚光焦點，在網絡上討論度極高。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3841102/org/14ec40a501391ba5ac36565ae8b615fa.jpg/x8SfkOD5Knxfpr4BDO6NGj-jHeUxl7TcQMM9yUDDPck?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3841102%2Forg%2F14ec40a501391ba5ac36565ae8b615fa.jpg%2Fx8SfkOD5Knxfpr4BDO6NGj-jHeUxl7TcQMM9yUDDPck%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=60bee655&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n廖思惟同沈月身為最亮眼的名媛之一，二人的背景亦不約而同地相似。在年齡上二人同是95後，廖思惟現年20歲而沈月今年就將滿19歲。在學歷上廖思惟目前在澳洲讀大學一年級，而沈月則在加拿大讀國際中學，據報導指她有意在爸爸沈嘉偉的時裝王國工作，所以擱置了到英國升學的計劃。<br />\n<br />\n在家庭上廖思惟的爸爸是廖鎮漢，是台灣知名百貨公司微風集團的董事長，旗下企業還跨足餐飲、自營精品同娛樂事業等範圍，是當地非常有地位之人。而她的媽媽孫芸芸亦來頭不小，其祖父就是有「中國電纜線之父」之稱的孫法民，爸爸就是台灣電訊公司台灣大哥大的創辦人孫道存，媽媽則是元大證券公司的副董事長，所以她從小就是千金小姐，在台灣當地屬於無人不曉的名媛。"},{"pid":"2f7e6983f664db32bcd7f41cc672050af3f80989","tid":1821013,"uid":29076,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T02:48:16.000Z","msg":"未夠班"},{"pid":"f50e54c45ce2003f1c4a372c116cb96b8d0c8ff6","tid":1821013,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T02:48:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3841157/org/8a74ee4c0481e4195015b0f977cb2d84.PNG/NQi3N65jx1-OlPbEnC8rVHhHY-pyOEiV0BDxJtAQ8SY?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3841157%2Forg%2F8a74ee4c0481e4195015b0f977cb2d84.PNG%2FNQi3N65jx1-OlPbEnC8rVHhHY-pyOEiV0BDxJtAQ8SY%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=c647a192&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今年即將滿19歲的沈月從小就擁有亮麗的外形，在她15歲的時候就已經公開亮相為聯合國兒童基金會拍攝宣傳照片，之後更為爸爸的品牌公司擔任模特兒在天橋上盡見光芒等。去年更出席被譽為世界十大奢華晚會之一的巴黎名媛舞會（Le Bal des D&eacute;butantes），以一身性感羽毛晚裝示人非常華麗，令她名聲再度急升。年紀輕輕應該升讀大學的她，據指擱置了到英國升學的計劃，全力幫爸爸打理公司業務，還不時擔任公司御用model，成為爸爸公司旗下品牌的「生招牌」。看來她已想清楚往後的目標是甚麼，絕對是一位美麗與智慧並重的美人。<br />\n<br />\n而她的勁敵廖思惟就不像她如此早公開亮相，現年20歲的她則在日前首度陪爸爸出席微風集團的尾牙，她一行出來即秒殺不少閃光燈。身穿碎花裙的她面對鏡頭顯得些少羞澀，臉帶嬰兒肥的她皮膚白哲，整體看上去氣質出眾，就是大家閨秀的模樣，對此不少網友對她有讚無彈。有網友在微博留言說：「肉肉的很可愛」﹑「圓臉好看」﹑最好看的明星子女」等，更直言比媽媽漂亮。<br />\n<br />\n而翻看廖思惟的社交網站，她亦不時非常大方地同大家分享生活日常。長相甜美的她據指身高167CM，經常大曬美麗長腿，而且她亦有運動的習慣練出小蠻腰。另外，據指她將有機會為爸爸集團品牌擔任代言人，幫自家公司做「生招牌」，潛力無限大的她是台灣當地最出眾的名媛代表。"},{"pid":"70fb6b875e316f3ba820b900a266167923c40da1","tid":1821013,"uid":209657,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T02:50:17.000Z","msg":"IG@trinityliao<br />\nIG@yuetyuetxx"},{"pid":"db12aac7ab615ab070d5ac545f35ef198a27bf7d","tid":1821013,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T02:53:11.000Z","msg":"正到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"893cecea37dc8284fdfd2ce33fb0fbbf1d68e67a","tid":1821013,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T02:55:47.000Z","msg":"對腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f81825d59a7ae317e7aec26b6cc788f1b20b68d9","tid":1821013,"uid":209657,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"db12aac7ab615ab070d5ac545f35ef198a27bf7d","tid":1821013,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T02:53:11.000Z","msg":"正到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T02:56:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2020/01/07/realtime/7302867.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=750\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2020%2F01%2F07%2Frealtime%2F7302867.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D750&h=daf97fc9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我覺得佢呀媽好似正啲.."},{"pid":"2af9fa86866f012ce6dc79d5a020dda015632a05","tid":1821013,"uid":209657,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T02:59:43.000Z","msg":"佢老母：<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2020-01-07/900/20200107004721.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2020-01-07%2F900%2F20200107004721.jpg&h=f713cf4e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.nextmag.com.tw//campaign/28/640x_e8618e1ca4adbddc0c340b965c7f5504.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.nextmag.com.tw%2F%2Fcampaign%2F28%2F640x_e8618e1ca4adbddc0c340b965c7f5504.jpg&h=e20255e0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6fd85f6f51104f8f543f01caff65b2c5c104bff7","tid":1821013,"uid":168941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T03:07:14.000Z","msg":"高下立見啦 好無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dbc28101b0a06a300923269bc41bee3b865ba47","tid":1821013,"uid":1712,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T03:23:11.000Z","msg":"孫芸芸正好撚多囉"},{"pid":"27b947526edd6981dbd46d450d87a4ce1fc390e4","tid":1821013,"uid":81684,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2f7e6983f664db32bcd7f41cc672050af3f80989","tid":1821013,"uid":29076,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T02:48:16.000Z","msg":"未夠班"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T04:01:46.000Z","msg":"人哋家底屌打喎"},{"pid":"a0e1e92ec1d79e1eaa221d52acb8e9026f9b8ae1","tid":1821013,"uid":165749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T05:33:56.000Z","msg":"食得下既"},{"pid":"ddd15376a4d041a85a18970e97be76f73a835d08","tid":1821013,"uid":124114,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T05:36:27.000Z","msg":"沈月正dd"},{"pid":"e61c33773b8b67bed82044178ee34826a91cd8d8","tid":1821013,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ddd15376a4d041a85a18970e97be76f73a835d08","tid":1821013,"uid":124114,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T05:36:27.000Z","msg":"沈月正dd"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T06:12:13.000Z","msg":"我都中意月月<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4500f7c33e7f336a96a4505184f7a66db64bec52","tid":1821013,"uid":152123,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T06:27:40.000Z","msg":"咁有錢+後生細女都著到成個老mk咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f83c85c2fa01da12c9c8cf3f006d53cd60737f31","tid":1821013,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4500f7c33e7f336a96a4505184f7a66db64bec52","tid":1821013,"uid":152123,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T06:27:40.000Z","msg":"咁有錢+後生細女都著到成個老mk咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T14:02:27.000Z","msg":"啊媽好後生"}]}